{"tid":54862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被遺忘的政治電影】皇家香港警察的最後一夜","createTime":"2016-12-26T01:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-10T12:45:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21dad47017231289a39d4982b74220049af64ded","tid":54862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"畀人遺忘的少有政治電影 <br />\n講皇家香港警察的最後一夜(1997年6月30日) <br />\nSEARCH舊POST,高登冇咩人討論,只有數年前影視台有巴打有少量討論 <br />\n有冇人睇過? <br />\n我剛剛網上訂了DVD <br />\n<br />\n一開始已經有金句出現,資金家歡迎共產黨,呢個世界都係無奇不有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一幕講解一個主權移交前警察殉職,97年6月30日出殯,死前蓋上的英國旗,被轉換成特區旗 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《皇家香港警察的最後一夜》早於2002年就拍攝完成了，塵封中跨越了2003年反對23條立法七一大遊行到2014年佔中運動這段崢嶸歲月，十餘年後才得以面世，卻如此一下子切入現實，就像是講述我們一段經歷的前世今生。 <br />\n電影圍繞香港回歸的歷史性交接瞬間，以上、下集虛構了兩個故事，同時以大量歷史實錄資料（包括當年 BBC 拍攝的港英鎮壓左派六七暴動片段，及一九八九年北京六四血腥震撼下的香港民運聲浪）穿插其間，讓虛構與真實之間模糊了界限。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LUwZHNKBwzE/VE2h6DLQuyI/AAAAAAAACzo/9i9xR0P4qC8/s1600/poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LUwZHNKBwzE%2FVE2h6DLQuyI%2FAAAAAAAACzo%2F9i9xR0P4qC8%2Fs1600%2Fposter.jpg&h=e57cfc8f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dI3AQiXh59g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdI3AQiXh59g&d=xFBgD7JdeVRjh0dh3SSrYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6b67f1db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dI3AQiXh59g</a> <br />\n《皇家香港警察的最後一夜》全集預告 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ACuMZg97hOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DACuMZg97hOE&d=xFBgD7JdeVRjh0dh3SSrYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a8a81dfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ACuMZg97hOE</a> <br />\n上集《一體兩旗》預告 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K9WPC4wX_sI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK9WPC4wX_sI&d=xFBgD7JdeVRjh0dh3SSrYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=66f23aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K9WPC4wX_sI</a> <br />\n下集《命運交響曲》預告"},{"pid":"a05780949eb808ed3bf8e71a793e5853cdf69ca1","tid":54862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"《皇家香港警察的最後一夜》導演劉成漢，是80年代香港新浪潮導演一員，也是著名影評人及講師；<span style=\"color: red;\">《皇家香港警察的最後一夜》從未正式上畫，甚或曾被香港國際電影師拒邀參展</span>，只曾推出過DVD和作非常有限量的放映，所以可能除影迷以外大眾完全未聽過的一部電影。其特別具爭議性之處，在於故事觸及六七暴動，劉成漢甚至從英國BBC搜集到香港政府從未公開過的六七暴動片段，並輯錄於電影之內。 <br />\n<br />\n電影分上下部份，第一部份《一體兩旗》以一名退休警察移民 (李隆基演) 之前，在離開香港啟德機場的車程中，跟他表弟回顧自己在六、七十年代時的當差生涯。那退休警察講道︰「若不是30年前他們「扑濕」班「左仔」，解放軍早就進了城。」說起來確有種以武力平亂有功之感。然後畫面上就見到當年民眾包圍港督府，爬上正門掛抗議條幅的紀錄片段，還有大量群眾間拳打腳踢、對警察掟石、焚燒雜物及群眾慌亂逃跑的紀錄片段，絕對比今天在旺角出現的零星衝突，暴力得多。 <br />\n<br />\n導演刻意將紀錄片段和劇情片段的交接模糊，讓觀眾更代入退休警察的回憶"},{"pid":"c2920fdefa2a0d49b77fe638a40a0ce770967f21","tid":54862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/26/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F2.jpg&h=05f1229e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/26/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F5.jpg&h=0f342b87&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n殉職警察被換上國旗 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/26/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F1.jpg&h=8b7e257d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一到12點,你就成為大陸走狗(對警察講)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/26/6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F6.jpg&h=81bb2c64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/26/10641214_884188344932456_5540677105002961438_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F10641214_884188344932456_5540677105002961438_n.jpg&h=94b27e0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6018fb6058331f23bea803360efc0a0980b4adf","tid":54862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"電影中金句: <br />\n<br />\n──資本家歡迎共產黨，這個世界真是什麼事都可以發生！ <br />\n<br />\n──五十年不變，傻子才信！人心都在變，凡事哪有不變的？ <br />\n<br />\n──再過幾年香港真不知會怎樣呢，七月一號之前，好歹有英國佬罩着；七月一號之後，就算共產黨不來搞你，香港這班新丁一上場，誰都知道會是什麼情況啦，肯定搞得雞飛狗跳！"},{"pid":"b28de7a654f8dd2a681f2873f83ad24424909d0f","tid":54862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:51:59.000Z","msg":"官方FACEBOOK <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rhkpmovie/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frhkpmovie%2F&d=xFBgD7JdeVRjh0dh3SSrYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=cdc961fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rhkpmovie/</a><br />\n<br />\n2002年電影,曾於早兩三年小量上晝戲院"},{"pid":"c09076767738b76f1aa6e851ad828173b120aae4","tid":54862,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電影中金句: <br />\n<br />\n──資本家歡迎共產黨，這個世界真是什麼事都可以發生！ <br />\n<br />\n──五十年不變，傻子才信！人心都在變，凡事哪有不變的？ <br />\n<br />\n──再過幾年香港真不知會怎樣呢，七月一號之前，好歹有英國佬罩着；七月一號之後，就算共產黨不來搞你，香港這班新丁一上場，誰都知道會是什麼情況啦，肯定搞得雞飛狗跳！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8d0392521b7d52b5d2bda096fcc9437df8e6c8","tid":54862,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一鍵留名"},{"pid":"4393a5387776dcca268e5e935dcc20fac850d45b","tid":54862,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"